name: The emka "Late Evening"
description:
Navy Unisex V-Neck Tee. Preshrunk white jersey knit. Deluxe 30's Soft style yarns. Non-top stitched 5/8 rib knit collar. Taped neck and shoulders. Mitered V-neck pattern. Euro style fit in neck, shoulders and sleeves. Double needle sleeve and bottom hems. Quarter-turned to eliminate center crease.
The back of this shirt is personalized with a woven tag on the bottom of the shirt with the manatee logo.
This item is packaged with our emka signature wooden round box. Boss!

name: Rebuild Bracelet
description:
If you've searched for the Refuge Clinic bracelet, you're in the right place! For every bracelet that is purchased, emka will donate $5 to the Refuge Clinic to help with supplies and other medical needs. Cool, right?! 
This bracelet has black beads with a black charm inscribed with Isaiah 58:12.
If there are any questions, please feel free to contact us on this project.
To learn more about The Refuge Clinic, go to http://www.refugeministriesky.org.
